  <div id="steps-section">
    <h1>Here are the steps that can get closer in achieving our dreams</h1>
      <div class="step1">
        <img src="image/form.jpg" alt="">
        <h2>Step 1</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fill out the form below.</li>
          <li>Mention the address from where we can collect the items.</li>
          <li>Kindly check the items you wish to donate(more than is allowed).</li>
